About Us and This Policy
Aventiv Technologies™ is a diversified technology company that provides innovative solutions to customers in the corrections and government services sectors. Aventiv® is the parent company of Securus Technologies®, JPay®, and Securus Monitoring®, (collectively referred to in this Policy as “Aventiv”), which are leading providers of innovative products and services. The collective power of these unified organizations delivers superior value and service to all of our customers nationwide.
This  Privacy Policy (“Policy”) applies to personal information collected by Aventiv and its subsidiaries through our websites,  mobile applications, and all products and services we offer  (collectively, the “Services”). This Policy describes our privacy practices, including how and why we collect your personal information and how we may use and disclose that personal information.
California residents may click
California Privacy Notice
to view our California Privacy Notice.
Your use of our websites, products, and Services constitutes your consent to these practices.
Collection and Use of Personal Information
We may collect personal information about you when you use our products and Services, mobile applications and websites automatically through cookies and other tracking technologies, and from our correctional facility partners. Personal information is information that, alone or in combination with other information, can be used to identify you as a specific individual (such as your name, email address, date of birth, postal address).
The table below sets forth the types of personal information we collect and how it may be used. The personal information we process about you may vary depending on your interaction with us.
