Government and Legal Authorities
To respond to lawful requests,
we may disclose personal information in response to lawful requests by government and other legal authorities, including requests from national security agencies, courts, and law enforcement.
Law Enforcement
To support law enforcement activities,
under appropriate circumstances, we may disclose your information to law enforcement personnel and/or correctional facilities and certain third parties for use in connection with and in support of law enforcement activities. All calls, visits, and communications using our Services will be recorded and may be monitored in accordance with applicable law, with the exception of calls to numbers and visits with third parties exempted from recording by correctional facilities. All of this data may be stored, monitored, searched, analyzed and transferred amongst law enforcement agencies for law enforcement purposes.
